{"tid":2507855,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東 10 歲男童點火燒 4 車 　「想看車爆炸飛起來」","createTime":"2021-04-28T09:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T10:17:41.000Z","uid":271829,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"758af2c575fbf40c313851a7481da77991b2854a","tid":2507855,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2940000/2943865/md-d54e59791c586766e0300841a24fc5e2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2940000%2F2943865%2Fmd-d54e59791c586766e0300841a24fc5e2_1024.jpg&h=abfca056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看電影不時都有各種爆炸場面，在現實生活中則很少機會看到。中國廣東省陽江市近日發生 4 輛自私家車起火事件。警方追查發現，燒車案件竟是一名 10 歲男童放火導致。男童被逮後坦承犯行，表示想看車爆炸飛起來，才會偷偷去點火燒車。<br />\n<br />\n據內地媒體報道，當地警察接獲報案，該區石灣村舊寨有 2 輛私家車著火，撲熄火警後，距離事故現場約 100 米處，還有一輛轎車車尾也有輕微燃燒過的痕跡，近日共計有 4 輛車被燒毀，令當地警方懷疑是人為蓄意縱火。追查發現，縱火的竟是住在附近的一名 10 歲男童。<br />\n<br />\n男童遭逮後立即承認，自己因電視上的爆炸事故覺得刺激，因此才點火燒車，想看汽車在眼前爆炸飛起來。根據中國法律規定，未成年人放火不予刑事處罰，會責令家長管教，但火災事故造成的賠償，需由家長或監護人負責。<br />\n<br />\n事件引來網民熱議：「希望他父母有錢賠」、「10 歲就放火了！這不是教育問題就是家教問題」、「平時不管教就是這樣的下場，唯一值得欣慰的是這孩子沒說謊」、「汽車沒爆炸，倒是他父母氣到爆炸」、「現在好了，輪到你爸爸飛起來了」等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2940000/2943865/380_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2940000%2F2943865%2F380_600.jpg&h=0fc512ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2940000/2943865/d5592669_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2940000%2F2943865%2Fd5592669_600.jpg&h=1afad996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2940000/2943865/d5592667_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2940000%2F2943865%2Fd5592667_600.jpg&h=f3cb0a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2940000/2943865/78640cb7845447de84243d42fb8dbfe3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2940000%2F2943865%2F78640cb7845447de84243d42fb8dbfe3_600.jpg&h=bd55c6e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6c91446f41a82795741c40c027b79a36f82303a","tid":2507855,"uid":270281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"噉有冇飛到"},{"pid":"34a6bace9747e7a9e07860d29abc0b41d25f7d9b","tid":2507855,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/62/a9/bf/62a9bf77105093d36566e38497ff86cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F62%2Fa9%2Fbf%2F62a9bf77105093d36566e38497ff86cd.jpg&h=6ab2666d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a44cb365fa251b22777f56a9ef54d9df50ac33a","tid":2507855,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"我都想睇 支持"},{"pid":"be0efc0c055872cdb0cf143c3727288c1b937d92","tid":2507855,"uid":54777,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"現在好了，輪到你爸爸飛起來了<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111bd3846948a28017c8a68a5847423d4c31f713","tid":2507855,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:53:52.000Z","msg":"國民教育"},{"pid":"131b9798754e36d2b4f01c4a7a474d4698dcae86","tid":2507855,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"「現在好了，輪到你爸爸飛起來了」<br />\n<br />\n多數係個老竇打到佢飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif